title: Tech to begin March with midweek clash against High Point - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech to begin March with midweek clash against High Point  VT hokiesports.com
description: Winner of six in a row, the Virginia Tech baseball team (6-0) will look to keep its perfect record in tact on Tuesday, March 1, when the Hokies welcome High Point (1-7) to English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park. Tuesday's 4 p.m. game between the Hokies and the Panthers will airÂ live on WRAD-FM 101.7 radio, featuring the play-by-play voice of Tech baseball, Evan Hughes.
